overview:
Cambridge Heat provides Home Comfort services and solutions to residents throughout Toronto and the GTA including Halton, Peel, Durham & Hamilton-Wentworth regions.

Cambridge Heating & Home Services sell, install and service a wide range of heating and cooling products with the sole purpose of providing the best in home comfort for your home or business in combination with superior customer support.

OUR PURPOSE IS TO SERVE: We are available to assist you with any issues you may have regarding your existing HVAC furnace or air conditioning system. Call us for any emergency service 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.
